SUMMARY:Meet Cute: La La Land
DESCRIPTION:Reaching for the same pair of black cashmere gloves? A chance encounter on a train? You never know if love is right around the corner! Introducing our new series “Meet-Cute” highlighting the best in cinema romances. \nWelcome to a world where dreams are made of jazz notes and a City of Stars! \nMia\, an actress who can’t quite catch a break\, and Sebastian\, a jazz purist who’d rather play in a smoky club than sell out\, collide in the most magical of ways\, in a land where romance dances as freely as the stars above. \nA love story filled with impromptu dance numbers on streets\, rooftops\, and even freeway overpasses! Between the swoon-worthy piano melodies\, stolen kisses\, and glitzy musical numbers\, La La Land reminds us that love isn’t always the happily-ever-after we imagine\, but maybe it’s even better\, a journey of passion\, and dreaming big… even if it means letting go.
URL:https://nowtoronto.com/event/meet-cute-la-la-land/
LOCATION:2236 Queen Street East\, 2236 Queen St E\, Toronto\, ON M4E 1G2\, Canada\, Old Toronto\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M4E 1G2
CATEGORIES:Film & Media
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://nowtoronto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/meet-cute-la-la-land.png
END:VEVENT
