SUMMARY:Comedy on the Run
DESCRIPTION:Fitness + comedy in one night! \nComedy on the Run – the perfect Thursday! Kick things off with a chill\, friendly 4km run—yes\, even the comedians are running with you—then roll straight into a comedy show. Refuel with a snack ticket\, sip on awesome drinks (boozy or not)\, and enjoy a night that perfectly blends feel-good fitness with big laughs. \nSociety Club House \nApril 2nd\, 6:30-8:30 \nRun lead by Sunday Pace \nFeatured comedians: \nJonathan Brent \nChelsey Grewer \nHeadlining: \nOussama Tabbara \nComedy show hosted By: \nRae Gallimore
URL:https://nowtoronto.com/event/comedy-on-the-run/
LOCATION:Society Clubhouse\, 967 College Street\, Old Toronto\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M6H 1A6
CATEGORIES:Comedy & Improv,Community Events,Fitness & Wellness
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://nowtoronto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/comedy-on-the-run.png
