SUMMARY:Question Everything Trivia @ The Castle on Queen
DESCRIPTION:Every other Thursday\, check out The Castle on Queen for a posh and proper Trivia Night! \nWHAT TO EXPECT \nYour hostQE owner\, and comedian Ari Issac (@summeroftong)brings the sass and laughs! \nGames \n\n10 trivia categories testing you on pop culture’s best and brightest celebs\, tv\, movies\, music\, and so much more!\nInteractive games mixed throughout testing your agility and wit for BONUS points!\n\nSpecials \n\nTBA\n\nWHO SHOULD ATTEND \nThink trivia isn’t your thing? Perfect – this is exactly for you. \nAt Question Everything Trivia\, we flip the script on your average game night. Forget boring\, brain-busting questions and awkward silences – this is trivia reimagined. Expect laughs\, sass\, and pop-culture madness that keeps everyone engaged\, whether you know the answers or not. \nWe’re inclusive\, welcoming\, and all about good vibes. \nPRIZES \nA $50 The Castle on Queen card for 1st place winners! \n1 Hour GRETA Unlimited Play Passes! \n* Additional prizes change on a week-to-week basis\, and are dependent on weekly sponsors and attendance. \nVENUE & TICKET RULES \n\nPlease arrive as close to 6:45 as possible to be seated so that the game can start promptly at 7PM\nOnce tickets are sold out\, please join waitlist to be the first to know if someone releases their spot last minute.\n$25 Minimum Spend / Person. This is just a couple drinks and food so it shouldn’t be hard to reach\, and helps the bar continue to provide these nights and epic prizes!\nFor groups of 6 people or more\, a 20% gratuity will be automatically added to your bill on the day.\n\n***IMPORTANT: RSVPS ARE NOT GUARANTEED SEATING*** \nRSVPing does not reserve you a spot or table! It is just to notify us and the restaurant that people are attending. \nThe restaurant has limited seating capacity\, so to guarentee your group a spot\, arrive early! Sitting is all first come first serve. \nPlease make sure you get to get there early to get the best possible spot. An RSVP is not a guarantee\, it’s dependant on space. We simply use RSVPs to gauge how many people to expect\, but of course as it’s a free event\, we sometimes have no-shows. We do what we can to accomodate everyone who RSVPs. If you are concerned about making the trip\, you can reach out directly to double check about seating\, and secure a reservation!
URL:https://nowtoronto.com/event/question-everything-trivia-the-castle-on-queen/
LOCATION:The Castle On Queen\, 884 Queen St E\, Toronto\, ON M4M 1J3\, Canada\, Old Toronto\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M4M 1J3
CATEGORIES:Games & Trivia
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://nowtoronto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/question-everything-trivia-the-castle-on-queen.png
END:VEVENT
