SUMMARY:All Vinyl Everything—Easter Thursday Edition w/Jester+Mastermind
DESCRIPTION:Thursday\, April 2nd marks the return of not one but TWO iconic DJ’s to All Vinyl Everything. \nBrown Eyes Entertainment in association with The Drake Hotel & DJAgile.com present:\nALL VINYL EVERYTHING\nNo Laptops. No Serato. Just Turntables & Vinyl.\nThe globetrotting king of clubs\, JESTER\, is coming back with his high energy vibes and deep musical knowledge. A master of all genres\, expect yourself to be locked in to his grooves from song one. \nAs well\, we welcome back the Canadian icon\, MASTERMIND\, for the rare vinyl DJ set. The radio and mixtape king was blasting through everyone’s speakers during the golden era of hip-hop. He pops out for the very special appearance exclusively at AVE. Absolutely not to be missed. \nAlongside resident DJ’s Mista Jiggz\, Agile\, and Mensa. \nThis is ALL VINYL EVERYTHING. \nThe Drake Hotel Lounge | 1150 Queen St. W. \nEaster Long Weekend – Thursday\, April 2\, 2026 \nDoors open @ 10PM \nLimited Early Bird tickets on-sale NOW – https://allvinyleverything.eventbrite.com/?aff=NP  \nFor booth reservations/bottle service\, call 416-531-5042. For group bookings/info.\, email info@browneyesentertainment.com. \nbrowneyesentertainment.com | thedrakehotel.ca
